When editing `e-paper-tg.ino`, always mirror relevant logic changes to `e-paper-tg.github.ino`.

Requirements for `e-paper-tg.github.ino` sync:
- Keep behavior/functionality identical to `e-paper-tg.ino`.
- Replace all secrets with placeholders (`YOUR_*`).
- Keep version and feature parity with the main sketch.
- Ensure `e-paper-tg.github.ino` remains non-compiling in Arduino builds inside this folder (template-only file).
